# Handle social media bots for listing pages - try multiple patterns
/listing/:listingId  /.netlify/functions/listing-meta?listingId=:listingId  200  User-Agent: facebookexternalhit*
/listing/:listingId  /.netlify/functions/listing-meta?listingId=:listingId  200  User-Agent: Twitterbot*
/listing/:listingId  /.netlify/functions/listing-meta?listingId=:listingId  200  User-Agent: WhatsApp*
/listing/:listingId  /.netlify/functions/listing-meta?listingId=:listingId  200  User-Agent: *bot*
/listing/:listingId  /.netlify/functions/listing-meta?listingId=:listingId  200  User-Agent: *crawler*

